_large.png?m=1331905828", "created": 1305871948, "last_modified": 1331905828}, "last_reply_by": "pokstay", "last_touched": 1643727276, "title": "诗词版 wordle 来啦，顺祝新春快乐", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/831568", "created": 1643680024, "deleted": 0, "content": "首先祝 V 友新春愉快！\r\n\r\n春节里，赶了个诗词版的 wordle 小游戏：\r\n\r\nhttps://peotik.com/\r\n\r\n玩法和 wordle 大同小异：\r\n输入一句诗词，给出提示，\r\n再根据提示调整输入，直到猜出当日的诗句为止，不过有回合数限制。\r\n每日（按 UTC 时间）一首诗词。\r\n\r\n暂时没有分享功能。", "content_rendered": "<p>首先祝 V 友新春愉快！</p>\n<p>春节里，赶了个诗词版的 wordle 小游戏：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://peotik.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://peotik.com/</a></p>\n<p>玩法和 wordle 大同小异：\n输入一句诗词，给出提示，\n再根据提示调整输入，直到猜出当日的诗句为止，不过有回合数限制。\n每日（按 UTC 时间）一首诗词。</p>\n<p>暂时没有分享功能。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1643680521, "replies": 17, "id": 831568}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1635652519", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1635652519", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 17862, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1635652519", "stars": 4517, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 237054, "username": "ac2064t", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ac2064t", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "shenzhen", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/61f69a7eb9b14a2769407f72943b7586?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/61f69a7eb9b14a2769407f72943b7586?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/61f69a7eb9b14a2769407f72943b7586?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1498315314, "last_modified": 1498315314}, "last_reply_by": "riotdandy", "last_touched": 1643734272, "title": "可以过渡用的盗版软件 for mac", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/831625", "created": 1643730141, "deleted": 0, "content": "这里给大家推荐一个 mac 平台的软件破解网站 https://macwk.com ，虽然是破解版的，但总的来说还过得去，目前用来没发现太大的问题（也没有主动去发现）。\r\n\r\n基本上的软件都有，只有个别的可能没办法，毕竟 xx 还要赚钱的。所以，何不一试呢？\r\n\r\n当然，还是要支持正版才好，偶尔使用下盗版的过渡也可以理解，大家各取所需吧。", "content_rendered": "<p>这里给大家推荐一个 mac 平台的软件破解网站 <a href=\"https://macwk.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://macwk.com</a> ，虽然是破解版的，但总的来说还过得去，目前用来没发现太大的问题（也没有主动去发现）。</p>\n<p>基本上的软件都有，只有个别的可能没办法，毕竟 xx 还要赚钱的。所以，何不一试呢？</p>\n<p>当然，还是要支持正版才好，偶尔使用下盗版的过渡也可以理解，大家各取所需吧。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1643730141, "replies": 17, "id": 831625}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_large.png?m=1524891806", "name": "google", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_normal.png?m=1524891806", "title": "Google", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/google", "topics": 2744, "footer": "", "header": "Google’s mission is to organize the world’s information and make it universally accessible and useful.", "title_alternative": "Google", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_mini.png?m=1524891806", "stars": 3327, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 65, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 34221, "username": "SharkIng", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/SharkIng", "website": "https://sharking.ca", "twitter": "XSharkIng", "psn": "", "github": "SharkIng", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "♥ 漫天飘鹤羽，清冷似冬凌", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e8756e76f9cae6cbe531ab8701c0a534?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e8756e76f9cae6cbe531ab8701c0a534?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e8756e76f9cae6cbe531ab8701c0a534?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1360950714, "last_modified": 1546923213}, "last_reply_by": "cest", "last_touched": 1643699186, "title": "GSuite 邮箱中邮件导出或下载问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/831559